headlines.description: — After lapping the field in the Eastern Conference, the Boston Celtics have the luxury of using the homestretch of the regular season to prepare for the playoffs.
headlines.shortLinkText: Murray scores career-high 44 points, makes game-winning shot in OT as Hawks outlast Celtics 123-122

events.name: Milwaukee Bucks at New Orleans Pelicans

headlines.description: — Zion Williamson took a more assertive approach to the final minutes of a close game and it paid off for the New Orleans Pelicans.
headlines.shortLinkText: Zion Williamson scores 28, closes out Pelicans' 107-100 win over the Bucks
